| [cargo](file:///Users/kaizenpro/Desktop/aether_nexus/nexus-core/src/cortex.rs#389-408) as library | `std::process::Command` subprocess |
| `ripgrep` crate | `grep-searcher` + `grep-regex` + `grep-matcher` |
| `mlx-rs` fictional APIs | Real 0.21 API: [from_slice](file:///Users/kaizenpro/.cargo/registry/src/index.crates.io-1949cf8c6b5b557f/mlx-rs-0.21.2/src/array/mod.rs#128-145), [as_slice](file:///Users/kaizenpro/.cargo/registry/src/index.crates.io-1949cf8c6b5b557f/mlx-rs-0.21.2/src/array/mod.rs#369-390), etc. |
