## Yellowpaper Invariants Verified

- ✅ [SparseCode](file:///Users/kaizenpro/Desktop/aether_nexus/nexus-core/src/types.rs#52-58) is exactly **16 bytes** (128-bit vector load)
- ✅ Fabric regions are **16 KB page-aligned**
- ✅ Regions are **non-overlapping** (verified by test)
- ✅ Genesis → Boot → Ed25519 Verify **roundtrip passes**
- ✅ `Pod + Zeroable` on all capability args/results
- ✅ Metal shader compiles to **metallib** via [build.rs](file:///Users/kaizenpro/Desktop/aether_nexus/nexus-core/build.rs)
- ✅ Cortex **rejects invalid capability IDs**
- ✅ Cold pool **casts to SparseCode slice** (zero-copy)
